  "elapsed_s": 31.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But this was his bad luck, because when the communists took power, considered him that he was a British spy and put him straight into jail, not considering that he was a anti-Nazi fighter.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "This was their interpretation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he suffered many years from the harsh treatment in jail.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But when he came back from the jail, through his very good background in the hotel industry and in the restaurant industry, he proved that he is a valuable asset for the Romanian tourist industry.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So he was put in charge of large hotels and restaurants.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Through this type of activity he managed to get contacts with people who were dealing with issuing passports in Romania.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So probably through bribing or other reasons, he managed in the year of 1969-- so a year after the occupation of Czechoslovakia by the Soviet army-- managed to obtain for Lillianna and I passports to visit Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "This wasn't considered a very big deal normally, because it was still inside the Iron Curtain.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was from one jail to another jail.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But in terms of Jews who applied for immigration from Romania and who were considered enemies of the regime, Lillianna and I couldn't get even this sort of passports.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So through her father we managed to obtain these passports.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And now we heard various stories about people who managed from Czechoslovakia which had a common border with Austria, which was considered the Western world.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "People managed to escape.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So in our minds immediately we made the plan.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we managed to save and buy a small motorcar in Romania after many years of waiting in a queue for buying such a commodity.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
